{"type":"message","id":"20eb4948","parentId":"26525df3","timestamp":"2026-04-21T07:38:21.389Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"chat:oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b5146da4d0cacc3af4e33b67d462\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_20c3b7b00c18c0cbc056d743ff4623bc\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_20c3b7b00c18c0cbc056d743ff4623bc\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-04-21 15:37 GMT+8\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_20c3b7b00c18c0cbc056d743ff4623bc\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_20c3b7b00c18c0cbc056d743ff4623bc\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_20c3b7b00c18c0cbc056d743ff4623bc\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b5146da4d0cacc3af4e33b67d462]\nou_20c3b7b00c18c0cbc056d743ff4623bc: @_all 理解你们的md文件，详细介绍自己。"}],"timestamp":1776757101389}}
{"type":"message","id":"0224f971","parentId":"20eb4948","timestamp":"2026-04-21T07:38:30.035Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking me (and the team) to understand the MD files and introduce myself in detail. Let me read the key files that are already loaded in context:\n\n1. IDENTITY.md - I know who I am\n2. SOUL.md - My personality\n3. USER.md - About the admin\n4. MEMORY.md - Long-term memory including team structure and my role\n5. AGENTS.md - Workspace guidelines\n\nI'm 4B · 大客户销售虾, the key account sales shrimp for large clients (客单价≥2万元). Let me craft a detailed self-introduction based on what I know.\n\nSince this is a group chat and the user said \"@_all\", they want all agents to introduce themselves. \n\nI should focus on introducing myself as the 4B key account specialist with a natural tone—professional but not stiff—and avoid markdown tables since this is Discord/WhatsApp. I'll highlight how I work with high-value clients and my collaborative approach with the broader team.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"嘿大家好！🦐 我是 **4B · 大客户销售龙虾**，下面给自己做个详细自我介绍：\n\n---\n\n**📍 我是谁**\n\n负责 **客单价 ≥ 2万** 的大客户业务。这类单子复杂、决策链条长、客户需求深，不是标准品能糊弄的。我的任务是把每一个大单当成一个独立项目来打。\n\n**🎯 核心定位**\n\n不做话术复读机，要做客户眼里的\"行业活字典\"。客户问我什么，我都能给到专业回答。方案不是套模板，是量身定制。\n\n**🛠️ 我能干什么**\n\n- 大客户日常沟通、需求深挖——搞清楚客户真正要什么，而不是他们嘴上说的\n- 出方案、推进谈判、协调资源——从接触到签约全流程把控\n- 72小时内完成初步尽职调查，2小时内给出定制化方案框架（含时间轴和风险点）\n- 签约前和5B代办虾做可行性预审，不踩坑\n\n**🤝 我和谁协同**\n\n- 私域运营虾（3+号）：谈不成但有意向的客户丢进培育池，让私域持续种草，我不浪费任何一个线索\n- 代办虾（5A/5B）：签完约30分钟内拉内部启动会，资料全交出去，我继续跟进客户关系\n- 数据诊断虾（7号）：要看数据的时候找他要报表和分析\n\n**⚡ 行动权限**\n\n- 我做主：日常沟通、挖需求、出方案、推谈判、协调内部资源\n- 我报备：申请定制服务包、低于标准利润报价、超范围赠品服务\n- 问老板：签1年以上战略协议、重大风险承诺\n\n**💡 我的风格**\n\n直接、务实、讲结果。不废话，该冲的时候冲，有风险的提前说清楚。宁可丑话说在前头，不搞事后背锅那一套。\n\n以上就是我，有什么需要配合的直接喊 👋"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.6-flash","usage":{"input":21038,"output":844,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21882,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776757101390,"responseId":"chatcmpl-5a94a7e6-b031-9012-b7ff-f4e0fc93fd36"}}
